<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Naaliatan's Accessories</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4f46e5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4f46e5;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #3730a3;
        }
        .info-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4f46e5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Naaliatan's Accessories</div>
            <h1>Thank You for Contacting Us!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{ contact.name }},</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to Naaliatan's Accessories. We have successfully received your message and our team is reviewing it.</p>
            
            <div class="message-box">
                <h3>Your Message Details:</h3>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Subject:</span> {{ contact.subject }}
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Message:</span><br>
                    {{ contact.message|nl2br }}
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Priority:</span> {{ contact.priorityLabel }}
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">Reference ID:</span> #{{ contact.id }}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Our support team will review your message within 24 hours</li>
                <li>You'll receive a response at {{ contact.email }}</li>
                <li>If your inquiry requires additional information, we'll contact you</li>
                <li>You can reference your contact ID #{{ contact.id }} in any follow-up communications</li>
            </ul>
            
            {% if contact.newsletter %}
            <div class="message-box" style="background-color: #e8f5e8; border-color: #28a745;">
                <h3>Newsletter Subscription</h3>
                <p>You've successfully subscribed to our newsletter! You'll receive updates about new products, special offers, and company news.</p>
                <p>If you didn't intend to subscribe, you can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link in our emails.</p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{ url('app_contact') }}" class="btn">Visit Our Contact Page</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Naaliatan's Accessories</strong></p>
            <p>Purok Mapahiyumon, Jose Romero Road, Junob</p>
            <p>Dumaguete City, 6200</p>
            <p>Email: support@naaliatan.com | Phone: +1 (234) 567-890</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Naaliatan's Accessories. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><small>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
